<header>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About GOV.UK Pulse</h1>
        <p>
            GOV.UK Pulse is a personal project of Jamie Magee that measures how British Government domains are following best practices for modern websites.
        </p>
        <p>
            GOV.UK Pulse is based off the project <a href="https://pulse.cio.gov/">Pulse</a> by the General Services Administration of the United States Government.
        </p>
        <p>
            GOV.UK Pulse is also an experiment built on automated tools, and is <del>probably</del> definitely not perfect. GOV.UK Pulse measures domains over the public internet using open source tools, and its results can be reviewed by anyone.
        </p>
    </div>
</header>

